\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
\lang english
Notes Field —
 Operational Narrative:
\series default

 The work order Notes field shall serve as the running operational narrative for the incident.
 The Information Operations personnel assigned to the work order shall enter all IoC observation detail,
 investigation activity,
 response decisions and their rationale,
 and actions taken within four (4) hours after the action is taken or before the conclusion of that staff member's current work shift,
 whichever occurs first.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
\lang english
Files Field —
 Evidence Artifacts:
\series default

 The work order Files field shall serve as the repository for all preserved evidence artifacts,
 including screenshots,
