 camera footage segments,
 and forensic captures attached to the record.
 If an evidence artifact exceeds the technical file-size upload limit of the System of Engagement,
 the Information Operations personnel assigned to the work order may store the artifact in a dedicated,
 access-controlled directory on an ECIO-managed secure file server.
 When this alternative storage method is utilized,
 the Information Operations personnel assigned to the work order shall document the exact network file path,
 file name,
 and the identity of the personnel depositing the file in the work order Notes field to preserve the chain of custody.
 Any such external storage location shall be subject to the identical access restrictions and retention schedules as the primary incident record.
\end_layout

